公用脚推了一下。saya就动手打人，saya的母亲不但不阻止并恶语相向，各种恶毒言语辱骂孕妇和肚子里的宝宝，最后导致这位怀孕32周+的孕妇高危早产入院，直到现在都没有脱离高风险早产征兆。然而saya就跟没事一般还 ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/19ff552b8275ce16_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot04\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/19ff552b8275ce16_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/61e7f4aaly1fv3mdo64xbj21kw22ehdx.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/19ff552b8275ce16_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">杨洋军艺<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">#杨洋0909生日快乐# 在今晚的成都生日会上，鲻鱼头造型亮相的@杨洋 开场便带来动感歌舞燃炸全场！首次钢琴Solo与粉丝齐唱《安心的温柔》，满满的感动。杨洋军艺时的同班同学也都全部惊喜现身为其庆生[憧憬]不仅晒出好多旧照回忆往事，还带来了杨洋父母写的信，超有爱惹~[太开心]http:\/\/t.cn\/RslSVpt ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n                <div class=\"UG_list_c\" action-type=\"feed_list_item\" href=\"\/a\/hot\/cf6ba27dcd8dc776_0.html?type=grap\" suda-uatrack=\"key=www_unlogin_home&value=hot05\">\n            <div class=\"pic W_piccut_v\">\n                <a href=\"\/a\/hot\/cf6ba27dcd8dc776_0.html?type=grap\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ww4.sinaimg.cn\/thumb180\/a716fd45ly1fv42ien0xaj20dw0rs0zk.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/a>\n            <\/div>\n            <div class=\"list_des\">\n                <h3 class=\"list_title_s\"><a href=\"\/a\/hot\/cf6ba27dcd8dc776_0.html?type=grap\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">教师节快乐<\/a><\/h3>\n                <div class=\"des_main S_txt2\">【谢谢你，老师[心]】“以前很怕你，现在很想你”，今天教师节，向老师说一声：#教师节快乐#！ ​​​​<\/div>\n            <\/div>\n        <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n    <div class=\"UG_box_foot\">\n        <a href=\"\/\/weibo.com\/a\/hot\/realtime\" class=\"S_txt1\" target=\"_blank\">查看更多<i class=\"W_ficon ficon_arrow_right S_ficon\"